<h2 id="htc-specialist">HTC Specialist</h2>

<p>HTC needed a way to create a deeper product understanding of the HTC One for it’s upcoming release, and wanted to move away from the expensive and ineffective print material they were using. Our solution was an augmente reality avatar, highlighting core value propositions of the device through interactive and visual storytelling. <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.digicave.htc.specialist.ar">HTC Specialist AR App</a></p>

