<h2 id="hello-magazine">Hello Magazine</h2>

<p>​Hello! Magazine has a readership of reaches over <a href="http://www.hellomagazine.com/marketing/marketing01.html">2 million adults in the UK every week</a>. For the Queen’s Diamond Jubilee, the magazine wanted something special for their readers. We captured Gary Barlow, the signer at the centre of the celebrations, to create the an interactive augmented reality cover. A worldwide publishing first.</p>

<!-- Note to Future Dom — formatting on auto save will break this file, because it will add extra /figuress at the end... -->

